name: Aerobic Dance
instructions: Start with feet shoulder-width apart. 2. Follow rhythmic movements combining steps, jumps, and arm movements. 3. Maintain continuous motion for duration. 4. Keep core engaged throughout.

name: Badminton
instructions: Hold racket with proper grip. 2. Move quickly around court. 3. Hit shuttlecock over net. 4. Combine footwork with arm movements.

name: Basketball
instructions: Dribble ball with fingertips. 2. Move around court with quick direction changes. 3. Include jumping, shooting, and defensive movements. 4. Maintain high intensity.

name: Battle Ropes
instructions: Hold rope ends with both hands. 2. Create waves by moving arms up and down alternately. 3. Keep core engaged and knees slightly bent. 4. Maintain rhythm for duration.

name: Box Jumps
instructions: Stand facing sturdy box. 2. Swing arms and jump onto box. 3. Land softly with bent knees. 4. Step down and repeat.

name: Boxing
instructions: Stand in fighting stance. 2. Throw punches (jab, cross, hooks). 3. Move feet constantly. 4. Combine offense and defense.

name: Burpees
instructions: Start standing. 2. Drop to plank position. 3. Perform push-up. 4. Jump feet to hands and explosively jump up.

name: Canoeing
instructions: Sit in canoe with paddle. 2. Rotate torso and pull paddle through water. 3. Alternate sides. 4. Maintain steady rhythm.

name: Climbing Stairs
instructions: Step onto first stair. 2. Push through leg to lift body. 3. Continue alternating legs. 4. Maintain steady pace.

name: Cross-Country Skiing
instructions: Slide skis in alternating pattern. 2. Use poles to propel forward. 3. Coordinate arm and leg movements. 4. Maintain gliding motion.

name: Cycling (Moderate)
instructions: Sit on bike with proper posture. 2. Pedal in smooth circular motion. 3. Maintain steady cadence. 4. Keep core engaged.

name: Cycling (Vigorous)
instructions: Sit on bike in aggressive position. 2. Pedal at high intensity. 3. Include sprints and climbs. 4. Maintain high heart rate.

name: Dancing (Fast)
instructions: Move to fast-paced music. 2. Incorporate jumps and dynamic movements. 3. Maintain continuous motion. 4. Let rhythm guide movements.

name: Elliptical Trainer
instructions: Place feet on pedals. 2. Hold handles. 3. Move in smooth elliptical motion. 4. Coordinate arms and legs.

name: Football (American)
instructions: Perform explosive movements. 2. Include sprints and direction changes. 3. Engage in physical contact play. 4. Maintain high intensity.

name: Golf
instructions: Walk between holes carrying clubs. 2. Swing club with rotation. 3. Maintain walking pace. 4. Include bending to place ball.

name: High Knees
instructions: Stand in place. 2. Run lifting knees to hip height. 3. Pump arms. 4. Maintain quick pace.

name: Hiking (Uphill)
instructions: Walk on inclined terrain. 2. Use full foot placement. 3. Maintain steady breathing. 4. Use arms for balance.

name: Ice Skating
instructions: Glide on ice with alternating legs. 2. Push off with each stride. 3. Maintain balance. 4. Include turns and stops.

name: Indoor Rowing
instructions: Sit with feet strapped in. 2. Pull handle to chest while legs extend. 3. Return arms first, then bend knees. 4. Maintain smooth rhythm.

name: Jump Rope
instructions: Hold rope handles. 2. Swing rope over head. 3. Jump as rope passes under feet. 4. Land softly on balls of feet.

name: Jump Squats
instructions: Start in squat position. 2. Explode upward jumping. 3. Land softly. 4. Immediately go into next squat.

name: Jumping Jacks
instructions: Start with feet together, arms at sides. 2. Jump feet apart while raising arms overhead. 3. Jump back to start. 4. Maintain rhythm.

name: Kayaking
instructions: Sit in kayak with paddle. 2. Rotate torso and pull paddle. 3. Alternate sides in rhythm. 4. Maintain forward momentum.

name: Kettlebell Swings
instructions: Stand with kettlebell between feet. 2. Hinge and swing kettlebell back. 3. Thrust hips forward to swing kettlebell up. 4. Let gravity bring it down.

name: Kickboxing
instructions: Stand in fighting stance. 2. Throw punches and kicks in combinations. 3. Move feet constantly. 4. Maintain high intensity.

name: Medicine Ball Slams
instructions: Hold medicine ball overhead. 2. Slam ball down forcefully. 3. Catch on bounce. 4. Repeat with power.

name: Mountain Climbers
instructions: Start in plank position. 2. Drive one knee to chest. 3. Quickly switch legs. 4. Maintain plank position.

name: Racquetball
instructions: Move quickly around court. 2. Hit ball against wall. 3. Include lunging and reaching. 4. Maintain high activity.

name: Rowing (Vigorous)
instructions: Sit with feet strapped. 2. Pull handle explosively. 3. Drive with legs then arms. 4. Maintain high stroke rate.

name: Running (6 mph)
instructions: Maintain upright posture. 2. Land midfoot. 3. Pump arms. 4. Keep steady pace.

name: Running (8 mph)
instructions: Maintain forward lean. 2. Quick foot turnover. 3. Powerful arm drive. 4. Sustain fast pace.

name: Shadow Boxing
instructions: Stand in fighting stance. 2. Throw punches in combinations. 3. Move feet and body. 4. Visualize opponent.

name: Skateboarding
instructions: Push off with one foot. 2. Balance on board. 3. Steer by shifting weight. 4. Include tricks if skilled.

name: Skiing (Downhill)
instructions: Position in athletic stance. 2. Turn by shifting weight. 3. Maintain balance. 4. Control speed with edges.

name: Soccer
instructions: Run continuously around field. 2. Dribble and pass ball. 3. Include sprints and direction changes. 4. Maintain high activity.

name: Spinning (Indoor Cycling)
instructions: Sit on bike with proper form. 2. Pedal at high intensity. 3. Include intervals and climbs. 4. Follow instructor cues.

name: Sprinting
instructions: Explode from start. 2. Drive knees high. 3. Pump arms powerfully. 4. Maximum effort running.

name: Squat Jumps
instructions: Lower into squat. 2. Explode upward jumping. 3. Land softly in squat. 4. Repeat immediately.

name: Stair Stepper
instructions: Step on pedals. 2. Alternate stepping motion. 3. Maintain upright posture. 4. Keep steady pace.

name: Swimming (Freestyle Moderate)
instructions: Stroke with alternating arms. 2. Kick legs in flutter motion. 3. Turn head to breathe. 4. Maintain steady pace.

name: Swimming (Freestyle Vigorous)
instructions: Stroke powerfully. 2. Kick aggressively. 3. Minimize breathing. 4. Maintain high speed.

name: Tennis
instructions: Move around court quickly. 2. Hit ball with forehand and backhand. 3. Include running and lateral movements. 4. Maintain rally.

name: Treadmill Running (5 mph)
instructions: Set moderate pace. 2. Maintain upright posture. 3. Land midfoot. 4. Keep steady breathing.

name: Volleyball
instructions: Move around court. 2. Jump to spike and block. 3. Dive and lunge for ball. 4. Maintain active play.

name: Walking (3 mph)
instructions: Step heel to toe. 2. Swing arms naturally. 3. Maintain upright posture. 4. Keep steady pace.

name: Walking (4 mph)
instructions: Walk at brisk pace. 2. Pump arms more vigorously. 3. Take longer strides. 4. Increase heart rate.

name: Wall Balls
instructions: Hold medicine ball at chest. 2. Squat down. 3. Explode up throwing ball to target. 4. Catch and repeat.

name: Water Aerobics
instructions: Move through water with various exercises. 2. Use water resistance. 3. Include jumping and reaching. 4. Maintain continuous motion.

name: Yoga (Hatha)
instructions: Move through various poses. 2. Focus on breathing. 3. Hold poses for duration. 4. Transition smoothly.

name: Yoga (Power/Vinyasa)
instructions: Flow through dynamic sequences. 2. Coordinate breath with movement. 3. Hold challenging poses. 4. Maintain continuous flow.

name: Zumba
instructions: Follow dance choreography. 2. Move to Latin music rhythms. 3. Include jumps and turns. 4. Maintain high energy.
